'''Eric Kabongo Ilunga''' (yavutse ku ya 21 Gicurasi 1984), ni umukinnyi wa filimi mububiligi n’umuririmbyi ukomoka muri Kongo. <ref name="brf">https://brf.be/kultur/kino/1048662/</ref> <ref>http://www.filmstarts.de/personen/776270.html</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime Welcome toGerany, ''Sawah'' and ''Third Wedding''. . <ref name="talenta">https://www.e-talenta.eu/members/profile/eric-kabongo</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 21 Gicurasi 1984 i [[Kinshasa]], muri Zayire (muri iki gihe [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo]] ). Afite imyaka 13, yaje mu Bubiligi bitewe nuko nyina yashakanye n’umubiligi maze atura mu mudugudu wa Flemish mu nkengero z’Ububiligi. Kuri ubu atuye i Waregem, muri West Flanders . <ref name="brf">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://brf.be/kultur/kino/1048662/ "Belgian Eric Kabongo is a cinema star in Germany"]. brf<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">1 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga we nk'umuraperi ufite izina rya stage 'Krazy-E'. Muri 2013, yabaye umukinnyi ufite uruhare rutemewe nkumugenzi wa gari ya moshi muri film ya ''The Fifth Estate'' . Mu 2014, Kabongo yagaragaye muri ''D5R'' hanyuma bahabwa uruhare mu kunenga yitirirwa Bubiligi film ''Black'' . <ref name="talenta">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.e-talenta.eu/members/profile/eric-kabongo "Eric Kabongo: Actor, Musician, Dubbing Actor, Model, Singer"]. e-talenta<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">1 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Mu mwaka wa 2016, yatumiwe mu [[Budage]] gukina nk'impunzi 'Diallo' muri filime isetsa welcome to Germany .  Hamwe na firime, yabaye umukinnyi ukomeye mu Burayi. <ref>https://www.moviepilot.de/people/eric-kabongo</ref> Muri 2019, yakinnye muri filime ''Sawah'' aho yatsindiye igihembo cya Golden Palm igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya film rya Queen Palm. Muri uwo mwaka, yakinnye muri seriveri ''Rivallen und Rebellen'' . <ref>https://peoplepill.com/people/eric-kabongo</ref><ref>https://www.filmweb.pl/person/Eric+Kabongo-2285920</ref>

Muri 2014, documentaire '''''What about Eric?''''' yarekuwe bijyanye n'ubuzima bwe. Nyuma documentaire yatsindiye ibihembo bya Best documentaire nziza. Hanyuma documentaire ''Ensor'' yatsindiye igihembo cya Best Flemish documentaire, nyuma yaje kwegurirwa Kabongo nabayobozi Lennart Stuyck na Ruben Vermeersch. <ref>https://www.friendspire.com/people/eric-kabongo/1471308</ref>

